<plot>Loosely inspired by the true story of Brenda Ann Spencer, a 17 year old girl who shot up a school and, when asked by the police why she did it, responded with "I don't like Mondays." Every so often we find ourselves saying "One of these days, I'm going to lose it and kill everyone." Claire has that day. From having coffee spilled on her, to discovering her boyfriend is actually engaged, to being yelled at at work, the little things add up until she just can't take it any more.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?375343</url></doc>
